lastVersion.statementHTML:
Goal

You work in fashion and want to know the most liked color of the moment. Many people answered a poll, and you now need to find the most excellent color.
Input
Line 1: An integer N for the number of people who answered the poll.
Next N lines: The colour they chose, one reply (colour) per line.
Output
One line: The most liked colour followed by the number of people who liked it.
Note: If more than 1 colour share the top ranking, output Multiple followed by the number of votes at which the tie occurred (e.g. red-3, blue-3=>tie number is 3).
Constraints
1 ≤ N ≤ 1000
Example
Input
5
Yellow
Blue
Blue
Green
Blue
Output
Blue 3
